Note on upstream content
------------------------
The dataset is a derivative work over public GitHub issues filed against
open-source agent-framework repositories. Each underlying issue remains
under its respective project's terms; this repository publishes structured
classifications + metadata, not verbatim issue content beyond what is
required for the labeled rows to be useful (title and a truncated body).
The CC-BY-4.0 license above applies to the structured corpus and its
classifications, not to the underlying upstream issues themselves.

